Description_lang: When your summoned Dreadstalkers fade away, they increase the damage of your Demonbolt by $s1% for $272945d.

description_blz.en_US: When your summoned Dreadstalkers fade away, they increase the damage of your Demonbolt by 10% for 8 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Cuando tus Acechadores nefastos se desvanecen, aumentan un 10% el daño de tu Descarga demoníaca durante 8 s.
description_blz.pt_BR: Quando os Espreitadores do Medo evocados por você desvanecem, eles aumentam em 10% o dano da sua Seta Demoníaca por 8 s.
description_blz.de_DE: Wenn Eure beschworenen Schreckenspirscher entschwinden, erhöhen sie den Schaden Eures Zaubers 'Dämonenblitz' für 8 Sek. um 10%.
description_blz.en_GB: When your summoned Dreadstalkers fade away, they increase the damage of your Demonbolt by 10% for 8 sec.

description_blz.ko_KR: 소환한 공포사냥개가 사라지면 8초 동안 악마 화살의 공격력이 10%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 當你召喚的恐懼潛獵犬消失時，會使你惡魔箭造成的傷害提高10%，持續8秒。
